songs.title: No Worries
songs.lyrics:
Yeah, hustle game, nigga!
T.I.P., K-I-N-G, Period, man
Zone one, West Side, A town, bitch!
Bankhead!

Look me in my face
I ain't got no worries, I ain't got no worries!
I ain't got no worries, I ain't got no worries!
See them Sh-roomies keep me up
So I ain't got no worries, yeah!
I ain't got no worries, I ain't got no worries!
You see money, right there
That's Tunechi, right there
Yeah, that's Mack Mane right there!
We ain't got no worries!
You see pussy right there
Redbone mangos, right there
See them sh-roomies, right there
We ain't got no worries

I ain't got no problem; nigga wanna get shot
I call him. nigga don't believe me, call him
Nigga, I'm ballin'. Nigga better be hauling ass
Can look good, then I put a chopper there
Blare, shawdy all about the cash
Nigga talk shit I laugh
Disrespect; you better watch it. We don't play about that
Take a nigga nigga's neighborhood; turn it into Iraq
Fuck that, I'm bad news! have you
Not heard about me, nigga?
Hey, I've killed careers in my years
And you not even good as these niggas
Catch me in the hood with these niggas
Fully automatic got a fifteen trigger
Pull up at the club, 'bout fifteen niggas
Everybody got a gun and a hustle gang sweater
Better? No! You can't see me, nigga!
I don't give a fuck about you and now I'm one of these niggas!
You can handle it when you see me, nigga
Do I look like I'm worried, nigga?

Look me in my face
I ain't got no worries, I ain't got no worries!
I ain't got no worries, I ain't got no worries!
See them Sh-roomies keep me up, (Hustle gang, nigga)
So I ain't got no worries (YMCMB)
I ain't got no worries, I ain't got no worries! (It's the king, bitch!)
You see money, right there
That's Tunechi, right there
Yeah, that's Mack Mane right there!
We ain't got no worries!
You see pussy right there
Redbone mangos, right there
And we ain't got no worries
